description: This Chainlink VRF common Chukcha purrs with a rating of 16, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 48, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, 2 for East, 5 for South, and Stringalong for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30163-62571-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [48 Votes, Common]
